projects.title: My Portfolio Website
projects.description: A personal portfolio website built to showcase my skills and projects using the MERN stack. It includes a custom homepage, project section, and contact form.

projects.title: E-commerce Platform
projects.description: An e-commerce platform built to sell products online. It features a shopping cart, user authentication, and an admin panel for managing products.

projects.title: Learning Management System
projects.description: A learning management system that allows educators to upload courses, assignments, and track student progress. It supports multiple user roles including students and teachers.
